videos.description: Florida forward Keith Stone gets the pass and powers his way to the basket for the and-1 layup.
videos.headline: Florida's Stone finishes through defender

videos.description: Esa Ahmad gets the pass off the turnover and throws down the big time one-handed dunk to give West Virginia their first lead of the game.
videos.headline: Ahmad flushes the dunk

videos.description: Florida moves the ball around the court and it eventually leads to a Keyontae Johnson dunk.
videos.headline: Good ball movement leads to Florida dunk
